    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring the variable valve timing operates within factory tolerances. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings for precise turn-in. While the finish shows light signs of enthusiast use, the drivetrain is robust, featuring a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. A mechanically sound, analog performance machine ready for the canyons.",
